N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 111.5 - Requirements for certified tree seed producers

State Regulations

Producers or collectors of tree seed to be certified must
comply fully with the registration or membership requirements of the
certification agency designated by the Commissioner of Agriculture and Markets
of New York for the certification of tree seed. Notes
